  "introduction": {
    "subtitle": "What risks would you actually accept? A risk menu across five life domains.",
    "description": "<p>Most people are not uniformly risk-taking or risk-averse — they have a palate. You may gamble with creative risk and recoil at financial risk. This quiz maps where your appetite sits across five domains.</p><p>For each scenario, choose what you would actually accept, not what you wish you would.</p>",
    "duration": "10 scenarios. Approximately three minutes.",
    "privacyNote": "Your answers stay in this browser. The result belongs to you. Sharing is your choice.",
    "disclaimer": "Original instrument. This is not a validated psychometric assessment.",
    "startButton": "Taste my risk palate"
  },
